Linux / Mac
===========
* git clone https://github.com/ebassett/dotfiles_vim.git ~/.vim
* chmod u+x ~/.vim/setup_vim.sh
* ~/.vim/setup_vim.sh

Windows (Vista or later)
========================
* git clone https://github.com/ebassett/dotfiles_vim.git %USERPROFILE%\.vim
* %USERPROFILE%\.vim\setup_vim.bat

